	<dita:topic xmlns="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="RU02-lnvxe_hierlev">
    <title>lnvxe:hierlev <lnpid>id-RU02-32030</lnpid>
    </title>

    <body>
        <p>
            <sourcexml>lnvxe:hierlev</sourcexml> becomes
                <targetxml>doc:metadata/doc:docinfo/doc:hier/doc:hierlev</targetxml>. </p>

        <example>
            <title>Source XML</title>
            <codeblock>
&lt;lnv:HIER&gt;
    &lt;lnvxe:hierlev role="ancestor"&gt;
        ...
        &lt;lnvxe:heading inline="false"&gt;
            &lt;lnvxe:title&gt;THE CIVIL CODE OF THE RUSSIAN FEDERATION, PART I&lt;/lnvxe:title&gt;
        &lt;/lnvxe:heading&gt;
    &lt;/lnvxe:hierlev&gt;
&lt;/lnv:HIER&gt;
	</codeblock>
        </example>

        <example>
            <title>Target XML </title>
            <codeblock>
&lt;doc:hier&gt;
    &lt;doc:hierlev&gt;
        &lt;heading inline="false"&gt;
            &lt;title&gt;THE CIVIL CODE OF THE RUSSIAN FEDERATION, PART I&lt;/title&gt;
        &lt;/heading&gt;
    &lt;/doc:hierlev&gt;
&lt;/doc:hier&gt;
	</codeblock>
        </example>
        
        <note>
            If <sourcexml>@level="1"</sourcexml> in source then, <sourcexml>@level="1"</sourcexml> attribute will become root or the outermost <targetxml>doc:hierlev</targetxml> and rest of the <sourcexml>lnvxe:hierlev</sourcexml> will become its child.
            For more clarification please refer the below example.
        </note>
        <example>
            <title>Source XML</title>
            <codeblock>
&lt;lnv:HIER&gt;
    &lt;lnvxe:hierlev role="ancestor"&gt;
        &lt;lnvxe:hierannot caption="THE CIVIL CODE OF THE RUSSIAN FEDERATION, PART I" level="1"
            role="ancestor"/&gt;
        ...
        &lt;lnvxe:heading inline="false"&gt;
            &lt;lnvxe:title&gt;THE CIVIL CODE OF THE RUSSIAN FEDERATION, PART I&lt;/lnvxe:title&gt;
        &lt;/lnvxe:heading&gt;
    &lt;/lnvxe:hierlev&gt;
    &lt;lnvxe:hierlev role="ancestor"&gt;
        &lt;lnvxe:hierannot caption="SECTION I. GENERAL PROVISIONS" level="2" role="ancestor"/&gt;
        ...
        &lt;lnvxe:heading inline="false"&gt;
            &lt;lnvxe:title&gt;SECTION I. GENERAL PROVISIONS&lt;/lnvxe:title&gt;
        &lt;/lnvxe:heading&gt;
    &lt;/lnvxe:hierlev&gt;
    &lt;lnvxe:hierlev role="ancestor"&gt;
        &lt;lnvxe:hierannot caption="SUBSECTION 3. OBJECTS OF CIVIL RIGHTS" level="3"
            role="ancestor"/&gt;
        ...
        &lt;lnvxe:heading inline="false"&gt;
            &lt;lnvxe:title&gt;SUBSECTION 3. OBJECTS OF CIVIL RIGHTS&lt;/lnvxe:title&gt;
        &lt;/lnvxe:heading&gt;
    &lt;/lnvxe:hierlev&gt;
    &lt;lnvxe:hierlev role="ancestor"&gt;
        &lt;lnvxe:hierannot caption="CHAPTER 7. SECURITIES" level="4" role="ancestor"/&gt;
        ...
        &lt;lnvxe:heading inline="false"&gt;
            &lt;lnvxe:title&gt;CHAPTER 7. SECURITIES&lt;/lnvxe:title&gt;
        &lt;/lnvxe:heading&gt;
    &lt;/lnvxe:hierlev&gt;
&lt;/lnv:HIER&gt;
        
    </codeblock>
            Becomes</example>
        
       
        
        <example>
            <title>Target XML</title>
            <codeblock>
   &lt;doc:hier&gt;
    &lt;doc:hierlev&gt;
        &lt;heading inline="false"&gt;
            &lt;title&gt;THE CIVIL CODE OF THE RUSSIAN FEDERATION, PART I&lt;/title&gt;
        &lt;/heading&gt;
        &lt;doc:hierlev&gt;
            &lt;heading inline="false"&gt;
                &lt;title&gt;SECTION I. GENERAL PROVISIONS&lt;/title&gt;
            &lt;/heading&gt;
            &lt;doc:hierlev&gt;
                &lt;heading inline="false"&gt;
                    &lt;title&gt;SUBSECTION 3. OBJECTS OF CIVIL RIGHTS&lt;/title&gt;
                &lt;/heading&gt;
                &lt;doc:hierlev&gt;
                    &lt;heading inline="false"&gt;
                        &lt;title&gt;CHAPTER 7. SECURITIES&lt;/title&gt;
                    &lt;/heading&gt;
                &lt;/doc:hierlev&gt;
            &lt;/doc:hierlev&gt;
        &lt;/doc:hierlev&gt;
    &lt;/doc:hierlev&gt;
&lt;/doc:hier&gt;     
    </codeblock>
        </example>
        <section>
            <title>Changes</title>
            <p>Created.</p>
        </section>
